name: BetaPro NASDAQ-100 2x Daily Bull ETF
longDescription: QQU seeks daily investment results, before fees, expenses, distributions, brokerage commissions and other transaction costs, that endeavour to correspond to two times (200 percent) the daily performance of the NASDAQ-100 Index R. QQU is denominated in Canadian dollars. QQU does not seek to achieve its stated investment objective over a period of time greater than one day.
